  <h1 class="tutorial-header">How to Use Mammoth Task</h1>
    <p>To master Mammoth Task.. First simply choose to Create a custom project or Manage your progress.
    </p>
    <img src="assets/createFirst.png" alt="Landing Page" />
    <p> We suggest if you are new to Mammoth taks to Create a new Project first.</p>
    <p> Input the Project Name and Choose a Due Date.</p>
    <p>As you add subtask they will automatically show up in the to the subtask list and in the calendar</p>

    <p>Go to the manage page to see updated project lists, due dates and subtasks. You can check the subtasks as complete, mark the Project as complete or even edit and Add the whole project by clicking on it's name</p>

    <p>When you are all done.. Delete the Project or leave it to see how much you've done!</p>


